snippet.title: Mario & Sonic at the Olympic Games Tokyo 2020 - All Characters
snippet.description:
This video shows gameplay with all characters in Mario & Sonic at the Olympic Games Tokyo 2020.  Time stamps for each character are listed below.

This channel features transformative & instructional video game guides, walkthroughs, speedruns & many other unique video creations.  My own personal creative input, gameplay and editing are clearly added into each video to ensure that all videos adhere to YouTube's partner program guidelines.  All gameplay is my own & is recorded and edited solely by me.  Permission to upload each game was provided by the game publisher.
